description: CertM: Table storing certificate management information for Ericsson radio access network elements.  dateTime: Timestamp of record creation. Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell. CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site. Id2: Redundant cell identifier. Id3:  Unknown identifier (likely a placeholder).
